OL,3,CSwansea hall re-opens with food stalls
OL,4,Cand bars after being shut for 15 years
OL,6,FAn old Swansea music hall that closed
OL,7,Fits doors over 15 years ago has re-
OL,8,Fopened as a foodhall and entertainment
OL,9,Fspace with a rooftop garden.
OL,11,FSwansea's Albert Hall has hosted the
OL,12,Flikes of Oscar Wilde and David Lloyd
OL,13,FGeorge over the years and was once
OL,14,Feven a bingo hall.
OL,16,FHowever, by 2007 it had deteriorated
OL,17,Fto the point where the building had to
OL,18,Fshut.
