OL,3,CSwansea hall re-opens with food stalls
OL,4,Cand bars after being shut for 15 years
OL,6,FNow the building is back open after a
OL,7,Fmajor restoration project costing
OL,8,Fnearly #9 million.
OL,10,FThe Albert Hall is now a four-storey
OL,11,Fvenue comprising a ground-floor food
OL,12,Fhall and bar, with private
OL,13,Fentertainment space, offices, studios,
OL,14,Fvisitor accommodation, a gym and a
OL,15,Frooftop garden.
