OL,6,FThe venue is on the fringe of the city
OL,7,Fcentre between The Kingsway and De-La-
OL,8,FBeche Street and not necessarily a
OL,9,Flocation where people gravitate to
OL,10,Fsocialise. But LoftCo Ltd, the company
OL,11,Fbehind the project are hoping this
OL,12,Fwill change.
OL,14,F"The maxim is, build it and they will
OL,15,Fcome", said director Simon Baston.
OL,17,F"The building is where the building
OL,18,Fis, and it's on the road to the train
OL,19,Fstation.
