OL,6,F"What we've tried to do is bring it
OL,7,F150 years forward but respect
OL,8,Feverything that happened 150 years ago.
OL,10,F"We wanted it to be a safe environment
OL,11,Fthat's family friendly and dog
OL,12,Ffriendly - something that works for
OL,13,Feveryone."
OL,15,FFood hall tenant Ali Tortorella, who
OL,16,Fis a joint owner of The Pizza Boyz,
OL,17,Fbelieves the building has "really good
OL,18,Fpotential" and thinks it's "going to
OL,19,Fbe very busy".
