OL,6,F"It's an up-and-coming area, and
OL,7,Fplaces like this seem to fill
OL,8,Fthemselves", he added.
OL,10,FLoftCo say the building will be an
OL,11,Fexciting fusion of history and
OL,12,Finnovation, bringing a much-loved old
OL,13,Fbuilding back into dynamic, modern use.
OL,15,FThe top floor of the 160-year-old
OL,16,Fstructure will feature new-style
OL,17,Fvisitor accommodation - known as an
OL,18,Faparthotel.
