OL,3,CSwansea hall re-opens with food stalls
OL,4,Cand bars after being shut for 15 years
OL,6,FEach room will be named after an
OL,7,Ficonic figure who's graced the old
OL,8,FAlbert Hall stage, including Charles
OL,9,FDickens & Oscar Wilde.
OL,11,FThere'll be exclusive meeting rooms &
OL,12,Fprivate dining suites named after
OL,13,Flegendary operatic singer Adelina
OL,14,FPatti who performed at the venue.
OL,16,FThere will also be eight street food
OL,17,Ftraders in the main hall, including
OL,18,FSwansea favourites and some new
OL,19,Fadditions to the city.
