OL,3,CSwansea hall re-opens with food stalls
OL,4,Cand bars after being shut for 15 years
OL,6,FFor families, there will be a
OL,7,Fchildren's jungle play area for little
OL,8,Fones to explore.
OL,10,FLeader of Swansea Council, Rob Stewart
OL,11,Fsaid: "They've done an amazing job
OL,12,Fhere of repurposing the old,
OL,13,Ftraditional Albert Hall. We're really
OL,14,Fpleased because it's a different
OL,15,Foffering to the city centre.
OL,17,F"It's great to see old buildings that
OL,18,Fhave been in the city for hundreds of
OL,19,Fyears getting a new lease of life and
OL,20,Fhopefully it'll become a really
OL,21,Fsuccessful venture."
